description: Nanoform Finland Oy engages in providing expert services in nanotechnology and drug particle engineering for the international pharma industry. The company is headquartered in Helsinki, Etela-Suomen and currently employs 87 full-time employees. The company went IPO on 2020-06-04. The Company’s affairs consist of both internal research and development activities and proof of concept type of research and development services provided to customers.
name: Nanoform Finland Plc
